<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 4 (Milla) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milla</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ジュード</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Jude</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>今度から肉を焼くときは気をつけよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll be more careful when grilling meat from now on.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱり灰はやりすぎだったね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I knew using ashes was just going too far.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>猟師というのは大変だな。
獣を倒したら必ず肉を食べねばならないんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It must tough being a hunter. Once you
defeat an animal,you have to be sure
to eat the meat, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>肉のない魔物はどうするんだろう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What do they do with monsters
that don't have meat...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>肉のない魔物は狩らないんだよ、ミラ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They don't hunt monsters
that don't have meat, Milla...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
